Interface JavaModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BioModule, ScriptModule
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ParserModule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddMetadataToOtuTables, Demultiplexer, JavaModuleImpl, JsonReport, Kraken2Parser, KrakenParser, MetaphlanParser, Multiplexer, Normalizer, ParserModuleImpl, QiimeParser, Rarefier, RdpParser, RegisterNumReads, SeqFileValidator, SlimmParser, TrimPrimers

    public interface JavaModule
extends ScriptModule
    Classes that implement this interface are pure Java modules.
